---
title: Double Pork Sausages & Sweet Mustard Onion Sauce with Potato Wedges & Nutty Broccoli Salad
description: This sauce is next-level amazing and will surely leave a big impression at your dinner time. How can it not dazzle with sweet caramelised onion chutney and dijon mustard combined together to go on top of herby pork sausages? Our mouths are already watering just thinking about it!
